            </div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container cta-section">
      <h2>Need Attestation Guidance?</h2>
      <p>Send us your documents and tell us what you need them for. We will advise on the specific attestation steps required and provide a quote for MOFA coordination and translation.</p>
